1. ACCEPTANCE OF TERMS

By accessing and using GymSuite ("the App"), you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provisions of this agreement. If you do not agree to these Terms and Conditions, please do not use the App.

2. DESCRIPTION OF SERVICE

GymSuite is a gym management application that provides tools for gym administrators to manage members, track memberships, process payments, handle enquiries, and generate reports. The service includes member registration, membership renewal, attendance tracking, and administrative dashboard features.

3. USER ACCOUNTS

3.1 Account Creation
- Users must provide accurate, current, and complete information during registration
- Users are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of their account credentials
- Users must notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of their account

3.2 Account Types
- Admin Accounts: For gym owners and administrators to manage gym operations
- Member Accounts: For gym members to access their membership information
- Trainer Accounts: For gym trainers to manage their assigned members

3.3 Account Termination
- We reserve the right to terminate or suspend accounts that violate these terms
- Users may request account deletion by contacting support

4. MEMBERSHIP AND PAYMENTS

4.1 Membership Fees
- Membership fees are determined by the gym administrator
- All fees must be paid in advance unless otherwise agreed
- Payment processing is handled through integrated payment gateways (Razorpay)

4.2 Refund Policy
- Refund policies are determined by individual gym administrators
- Disputes regarding payments should be resolved directly with the gym

4.3 Automatic Renewal
- Memberships may be set to automatically renew based on gym policies
- Users will be notified before automatic renewal charges

5. DATA COLLECTION AND PRIVACY

5.1 Information Collected
- Personal information: Name, email, contact number, date of birth
- Membership details: Membership type, start date, end date, payment history
- Photos: Profile pictures and ID documents uploaded by users
- Usage data: App activity, attendance records, payment transactions

5.2 Use of Information
- To provide and improve our services
- To process payments and manage memberships
- To communicate important updates and notifications
- To generate reports and analytics for gym administrators

5.3 Data Storage
- Data is stored securely using Firebase Cloud Firestore and Firebase Storage
- We implement industry-standard security measures to protect user data
- Data is encrypted during transmission and at rest

5.4 Data Sharing
- We do not sell or share personal data with third parties for marketing purposes
- Data may be shared with payment processors for transaction processing
- Gym administrators have access to their members' data for management purposes

5.5 Data Retention
- User data is retained as long as the account is active
- Deleted accounts and associated data are permanently removed within 30 days
- Financial records may be retained longer for legal and accounting purposes

